2002-2007 (La. 10/25/02)

Noemi B. OLIVER v. TRANSPORT SERVICE COMPANY. No. 2002-C-2007. Supreme Court of Louisiana. Oct. 25, 2002.

*1158In re Transport Service Company; — Defendant; Applying for Writ of Certiorari and/or Review Office Of Workers’ Compensation District 05, No. 99-06837; to the Court of Appeal, First Circuit, No. 2001 CA 0681.

Denied.

VICTORY, J., would grant on attorneys’ fees. TRAYLOR, J., would grant on attorneys’ fees.
